comment.body:
This popup looks like an ad (it redirects to third-party website when clicked), so could you please move it to - https://github.com/AdguardTeam/AdguardFilters/blob/master/BaseFilter/sections/specific.txt

Also please add spaces before `!important`, like:
```adblock
circleofcricket.com#$#body { overflow: visible !important; }
circleofcricket.com#$#.modal-backdrop { display: none !important; }
circleofcricket.com#$##myModal { display: none !important; }
```
It's not an issue, but as far as I know, we prefer to add it this way.
